    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six equipped with six individual throttle bodies. This specimen has undergone a comprehensive technical refresh, including a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul and a precise valve shim adjustment to ensure optimal valvetrain harmonics. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, delivering power to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with proactive subframe reinforcement and fresh OEM bushings throughout. The exterior retains its factory paint depth and mirror-like finish, while the Nappa leather interior shows no bolster wear or UV degradation. A turn-key example for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 49200.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
